Want to emulate Millie Mackintosh's bohemian summer style? Now you can, because the Made In Chelsea star-turned-designer has just released even more designs from her hotly anticipated fashion range.

The 25-year-old has added to her spring/summer 15 range - and there's feminine lace dresses, cool khaki jackets and a peach jumpsuit perfect for the festival season.

Speaking to FEMAIL about her new collection of suede dresses and tasseled jackets, the stylish star said: 'The range was inspired by my love of festivals and it has a real 70s influence.

'It's full of easy-to-wear shapes, feminine patterns and playful prints.' 

