As well as style expertise, Millie, who trained as a make-up artist before finding fame, is a beauty buff with her own eyelash range.

Sharing her top beauty tips for flawless summer skin, the star - a self-confessed sun worshiper - says SPF is essential.

'I loved sunbathing all my life and now I am so worried about sun damage so I always wear a tinted moisturiser with an SPF in and some cream bronzer and pastel eyeshadow for a natural sunkissed look.'

